name: PHC-WIN
tagline: Create single executables for your PHP applications
body:
# PHC-WIN #

## What is it? ##

PHC-WIN create single executables out of you PHP applications, and includes the WinBinder & win32std extensions.

## Supported OS's ##
  - Windows XP (w/ self compiled PHP versions)
  - Windows Server 2003
  - Windows Vista
  - Windows 7
  - Windows 8

## Authors ##
  - [Jared Allard] (https://jaredallard.me)
